    "question": "During testing of your multi-agent research system, you notice that the web search agent occasionally fails to invoke its designated MCP tool for web searches, even when the query clearly matches the tool's description and input format. This happens sporadically but consistently enough to be a concern. What is the most effective mitigation strategy?",
